Here is the command to load the file from local machine to Hadoop system, 
command 
Hadoop fs -copyFromLocal /home/cloudera/hadoopTrainig.txt /user/cloudera
to check the file in the Hadoop cluster you can  see 
hadoop fs -ls /user/cloudera
